class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639fbd7967fdc283d0325d6861e1709f835b0406","tid":1379542,"uid":79181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:49:27.000Z","msg":"Twitch疑向中共跪低！直播香港示威帳號永久封鎖 輸入1989等字眼被禁言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbfe6a81a538a384daec70453b79a89e7bffe74d","tid":1379542,"uid":82067,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:51:59.000Z","msg":"幫佢地加速得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35928e02e4fd7bd5f810bef3d39fad28b02aadf","tid":1379542,"uid":276865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:58:32.000Z","msg":"今日見到佢地係射擊支援+重兵推進縮短再騎兵收割, 期間射擊支援係無停過"},{"pid":"fd2aae00ec69d6833c8f0642bb61d594577d37b0","tid":1379542,"uid":52105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cd2b180a3843c37cfdfecc4066e1c5acad13e1","tid":1379542,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:59:10.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"e07fa1a7e60fa1538fc57f384178ed35cde8fe4b","tid":1379542,"uid":57771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"b01ba6c1ab5df0ca3aa24a538c5786613a6468c8","tid":1379542,"uid":274165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7eac14de4289f4a2de52f0099c6d7f6c6d592c7a","tid":1379542,"uid":113163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<strong>等我又發表下係睇法睇下幫唔幫到手<br />\n<br />\n係尋晚電視到睇到POPO既推進模式 <br />\n<br />\n先有第一手排長盾&gt; 對峙&gt;TG<br />\n等到有增援包括更多鎮暴 及速龍<br />\n會等速龍搵目標<br />\n<br />\n會再射一輪TG, cover 速龍推進<br />\n速龍輕裝會快到 等捉到手足後其他鎮暴先到 尋日起碼有兩次用咁既模式推進<br />\n每次大約70到100米<br />\n<br />\n往往示威者得一層防線 但欠深度<br />\n示威者大多人迫埋一齊 後面走唔切最前既手足走唔到 就被捉<br />\n<br />\n從理論上係咪可以諗下set第二防線 相差30米左右 唔好迫住比手足有位走 同第二防線用黎cover第一防線既手足？<br />\n<br />\n前線既手足係想setup hold Point,定係想打持久？<br />\n<br />\n如果想setup hold Point, 裝備上好難對抗<br />\n<br />\n如果打持久更應靈活<br />\n<br />\n原諒我係和理及冷氣軍師 我只係想諗下有無野幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"cc786da16923273c66b5226b506175acd51869a2","tid":1379542,"uid":112910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d41c3fbddd3d491ea55445a8dee7b4385a7d768","tid":1379542,"uid":191312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce1f7881617f39a3f6ecf8a02ac345192c0e5733","tid":1379542,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6612fb834494f9bce39419d4c5b84e375d9df39c","tid":1379542,"uid":24615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a35928e02e4fd7bd5f810bef3d39fad28b02aadf","tid":1379542,"uid":276865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:58:32.000Z","msg":"今日見到佢地係射擊支援+重兵推進縮短再騎兵收割, 期間射擊支援係無停過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"正常情況 出恐龍短兵相接就應該會停射擊支援 因為會打中自己人"},{"pid":"6cde7d222dce8a651407857d2199c4aadb05153e","tid":1379542,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ee5bcb2eb70926167634428995a92440bbd2f14","tid":1379542,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d0e0c1efebb6f0e3ba085fa345c920dc68d3c81","tid":1379542,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"等陣可能講下咩叫波動進攻（即係人海戰術）<br />\n具體係點玩<br />\n<br />\n示威者 人數多 攻擊力低